  2037→            function getRelativeTimeString(date) {
  2038→                const now = new Date();
  2039→                const diffMs = now - date;
  2040→                const diffDays = Math.floor(diffMs / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));
  2041→                
  2042→                if (diffDays < 1) return 'Today';
  2043→                if (diffDays < 2) return 'Yesterday';
  2044→                if (diffDays < 7) return `${diffDays} days ago`;
  2045→                if (diffDays < 30) return `${Math.floor(diffDays / 7)} weeks ago`;
  2046→                if (diffDays < 365) return `${Math.floor(diffDays / 30)} months ago`;
  2047→                return `${Math.floor(diffDays / 365)} years ago`;
  2048→            }
  2049→        });

            function updateURLParameters(category, subcategory, language, maintenance, search) {
                const params = new URLSearchParams();

                if (category) params.set('category', category);
                if (subcategory) params.set('subcategory', subcategory);
                if (language) params.set('language', language);

                // Update URL without page reload
                const newURL = params.toString() ?
                    `${window.location.pathname}?${params.toString()}` :
                    window.location.pathname;
                window.history.replaceState({}, '', newURL);
